Package de.elo.ix.client.subs

Class CheckoutSubstitutionsInfo

java.lang.Object
byps.BValueClass
de.elo.ix.client.ValueClass
de.elo.ix.client.subs.CheckoutSubstitutionsInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class CheckoutSubstitutionsInfo
extends ValueClass
This object is used to define which substitutions should be returned by IXServicePortIF.checkoutSubstitutions(de.elo.ix.client.ClientInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.CheckoutSubstitutionsInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.SubstitutionZ, de.elo.ix.client.LockZ).

The elements in one list are always search with an OR operation. If various list are provided, they are connected using OR (default) (set andOperator to true to use AND operator)

Since:
12.00.000.026
